user.biography: • B’HOOD IS SOMETHING YOU CREATE WITHIN YOURSELF BY BELIEVING IN WHO YOU ARE • I AM B'HOOD • BE YOU, BRAVELY •

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by B' H O O D on August 29, 2021. May be an image of one or more people and brick wall.

node.text: • YOUR GREATEST AWAKENING COMES • WHEN YOU BECOME AWARE ABOUT YOUR  INFINITE NATURE • YOUR CONNECTION TO DIVINE CONSCIOUSNESS • IN EACH OF US THERE EXISTS A CLEAR • WIDER PERSPECTIVE OF REALITY • A GREATER LEVEL OF KNOWING • MORE FREEDOM • GREATER POWER • MORE OPPORTUNITY TO CREATE • AND DIRECT YOUR OWN MIND TO WHATEVER ENDS YOU MIGHT DESIRE • I AM B’HOOD • BE YOU, BRAVELY •

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by B' H O O D on August 22, 2021. May be a closeup.

node.text: • TRANSCENDENCE AND TRANSFORMATION OF CONSCIOUSNESS WILL CREATE A NEW REALITY • CHOOSE WHO YOU WANT TO BECOME • RECLAIM YOUR AWARENESS • AND YOU WILL BEGIN TO SHIFT INTO THAT VERSION OF YOURSELF • YOU MUST MASTER A NEW WAY OF THINKING • BEFORE YOU MASTER A NEW WAY OF BEING • IT IS YOU WHO IS THE MASTER MAGICIAN OF YOUR LIFE • I AM B’HOOD • BE YOU, BRAVELY

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by B' H O O D on August 15, 2021. May be an image of one or more people.

node.text: • WE ARE ALL ESSENCE OF THE DIVINE • THE SPIRITUAL JOURNEY IS THE UNLEARNING OF THE MENTAL SLAVERY FROM SOCIAL PROGRAMMING • THE PROCESS OF WHICH THE IDEAS • CONCEPTS AND BELIEFS OF THE SOCIETY IN WHICH WE LIVE ARE INGRAINED INTO OUR PSYCHE • CONFORMITY IS THE JAILER OF FREEDOM AND ENEMY TO ENLIGHTENMENT • DO NOT CONFORM TO THE PATTERN OF THIS WORLD • BUT BE TRANSFORMED BY THE RENEWING OF YOUR MIND • I AM B’HOOD • BE YOU, BRAVELY •

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by B' H O O D on August 09, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and tattoo.

node.text: VIS•U•AL•IZE • FORM A MENTAL IMAGE AND MAKE IT VISIBLE TO THE MINDS EYE • I AM B’HOOD • BE YOU, BRAVELY •

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by B' H O O D on August 03, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and brick wall.

node.text: • YOU HAVE TO REPROGRAM YOUR MIND • TO GAIN YOUR SPIRITUAL SENSE • LET THE UNIVERSE HEAR YOUR DREAMS • AND WATCH WHAT BEGINS TO UNFOLD • I AM B’HOOD • BE YOU, BRAVELY •

node.text: THE WAY YOU EXPERIENCE THE WORLD AROUND YOU IS A DIRECT REFLECTION OF THE WORLD WITHIN YOU • YOU ARE NOT LIMITED BY YOUR SOCIOECONOMIC STATUS OR LIFE CIRCUMSTANCES • YOU ARE LIMITED BY YOUR BELIEFS • FEARS • DOUBTS • EMOTIONAL WOUNDS AND SELF SABOTAGE PATTERNS • THE TRUTH IS NO MATTER WHAT YOUR CURRENT CIRCUMSTANCES • IF YOU CAN IMAGINE SOMETHING BETTER FOR YOURSELF YOU CAN CREATE IT • THE INNER REALMS OF THE MINDS EYE IS A PLAYGROUND AND CANVAS FOR CONSCIOUSNESS TO EXPLORE CREATION • WHEN WE GO INTO OUR IMAGINATION CONSCIOUSLY • WE CAN FOCUS ON REALITIES THAT WE WANT TO SEE MORE OF • WE ARE LITERALLY SCULPTING AND MOLDING OUR NEW REALITIES FROM WITHIN THE REALMS OF THE IMAGINATION BEFORE THEY ARE EVER MADE MANIFEST WITHIN THE DIMENSIONS OF FORM • I AM B’HOOD • BE YOU, BRAVELY • #BHOOD • #BROTHERHOOD •

node.text: • HUMANS WALK THROUGH LIFE LOOKING FOR A KEY THATS ALREADY WITHIN THEM • REALITY AS YOU EXPERIENCE IT IS SIMPLY A REFLECTION OF YOUR CURRENT LEVEL OF CONSCIOUSNESS • BY EXPANDING YOUR CONSCIOUSNESS • YOUR ABLE TO CULTIVATE YOUR DESIRED REALITY • AT THE CENTER OF EVERY PERSON LIES THE HIDDEN SPARK OF DEVINE WAITING TO BE EXPLORED AND EXPRESSED • I AM B’HOOD • BE YOU, BRAVELY • #BHOOD •

node.text: • WE CANNOT KNOW THE HIGHEST EXPRESSION OF ARE NATURE • UNTIL WE KNOW THE DEEPEST INNER CONTENTS OF ARE OWN BEING • SELF STUDY IS SELF MASTERY AND IS THE PATH WAY TO EXPANDING CONSCIOUSNESS AND ARE HIGHER SELF • ONLY BY LETTING GO OF ALL PHYSICAL AND MENTAL LIMITS ARE YOU FREE TO EXPERIENCE THE TRUTH OF YOUR EXISTENCE • THE ONLY LIMITS THAT EXIST ARE THE ONES YOU CREATE • I AM B’HOOD • BE YOU, BRAVELY •

node.text: • SOMETIMES WE CHOOSE TO STAY HIDDEN IN LIFE AND SILENCE OURSELVES OUT OF FEAR OF BEING SEEN • FEAR OF BEING REPRIMANDED • NOT TRUSTING OURSELVES • NOT FEELING SAFE ENOUGH TO SPEAK • OR EVEN A FEAR OF BEING VULNERABLE • WHEN YOU SILENCE YOURSELF • YOU BECOME A BACKGROUND CHARACTER IN YOUR OWN STORY • YOUR THOUGHTS • WISDOM • AND EXPERIENCES ARE SECONDARY TO THE WORLD TELLING YOU WHAT YOUR EXPERIENCE SHOULD BE • YOU SHUT OUT YOUR PERSONALITY AND THE GIFTS YOU’RE HERE TO SHARE BECAUSE ITS SAFER TO FIT IN AND NOT DEVIATE FROM SOCIALLY ACCEPTED RULES AND NORMS • EVEN THOUGH YOU’RE HERE TO EXPAND TO FULL CAPACITY • WE CAN USE OUR COMMUNICATION TO SET OURSELVES APART • OR TO CONFORM TO THE STATUS QUO • THERE IS AN ILLUSION OF SAFETY WITH FITTING IN • BUT IT COMES AT THE COST OF SILENCING YOURSELF • WHICH UNDERMINES A PERSON’S WILL • TRUTH • AND AUTHENTICITY • I AM B’HOOD • BE YOU, BRAVELY •

node.text: • DON’T BE IMPRISONED BY OTHERS PERCEPTION OF REALITY • YOU DON’T HAVE TO LIVE IN ANYONE’S SHADOW • ALLOW YOUR UNIQUE CHARACTERISTICS TO SHINE FORTH AND ILLUMINATE YOUR WAY • THE WORLD WE LIVE IN • THE LIFE WE PERCEIVE • IS A PERFECT REFLECTION • A MIRROR IMAGE • OF OUR INTERNAL REALITY • PERCEPTION IS THE BEGINNING OF ALL REALIZATION AND ACTUALIZATION OF POSSIBILITIES • I AM B’HOOD • BE YOU, BRAVELY •
